OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FBaby Pippa's father Thomas Gillibrand
OL,7,Fsaid a hospital's home birth service
OL,8,Fplayed "Russian roulette" with the
OL,9,Flives of mothers and babies.
OL,11,FThe father of a baby who died after a
OL,12,Fplanned home birth went wrong has
OL,13,Faccused his local hospital of playing
OL,14,F"Russian Roulette" with the lives of
OL,15,Fmothers and babies.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@YO]
