OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FVictoria Gillibrand, 33, had planned
OL,7,Fto give birth to baby Pippa at her
OL,8,Fhome in Warrington, but when she went
OL,9,Finto labour, the home birth team were
OL,10,Fattending another labour, an inquest
OL,11,Fat Cheshire Coroner's Court was told.
OL,13,FCoroner Victoria Davies found there
OL,14,Fwere "missed opportunities" for
OL,15,FWarrington and Halton Hospitals NHS
OL,16,FFoundation Trust to suspend the home
OL,17,Fbirth service and tell Mrs Gillibrand
OL,18,Fto come into hospital.
OL,26,@vD@FOUvD@[O]
