OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FPippa, who was born 25 August 2024,
OL,7,Fdied at 12 days old, after suffering a
OL,8,Fsevere brain injury due to the
OL,9,F"avoidable delay" in delivery, the
OL,10,Fcoroner's court was told.
OL,12,FMs Davies said she planned to write to
OL,13,Fthe Health Secretary Wes Streeting,
OL,14,FNHS England and the National Institute
OL,15,Ffor Health and Care Excellence (Nice)
OL,16,Fto raise concerns about the lack of
OL,17,Fnational guidance for home birth
OL,18,Fservices.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@QO]
