OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FSpeaking outside the coroner's court
OL,7,Fin Warrington, Pippa's father Thomas
OL,8,FGillibrand, 34, said: "The trust seems
OL,9,Fto have played Russian roulette with
OL,10,Fthe innocent lives of mothers and
OL,11,Fbabies.
OL,13,F"Tragically, we are the family that
OL,14,Ftook the bullet on that. Our feelings
OL,15,Fare that Pippa's death was clearly
OL,16,Fpreventable and it shouldn't have
OL,17,Ftaken a child's death for changes to
OL,18,Fbe implemented."
OL,26,@pD@WOUuD@AOUzD@PO]
