OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FMrs Gillibrand, who carried a small
OL,7,Ftoy bought for Pippa with her, added:
OL,8,F"Services have been underfunded and
OL,9,Fstretched for such a long time, that
OL,10,Fwe're now in a position that we've
OL,11,Flost our daughter because of the cuts
OL,12,Fand the services that are currently in
OL,13,Fsitu, and things need to change."
OL,15,FThe inquest heard Mr Gillibrand called
OL,16,FWarrington Hospital at about 5.30am on
OL,17,Fthe Sunday of the August bank holiday
OL,18,Fweekend to tell them his wife was in
OL,19,Flabour.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@aO]
