OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FDelivering her findings, the coroner
OL,7,Fsaid: "In light of the staffing
OL,8,Fissues, including that the home birth
OL,9,Fteam were already at another birth,
OL,10,FPippa's mother should have been
OL,11,Fadvised to attend hospital rather than
OL,12,Fcontinue as a home birth."
OL,14,FShe said there was another missed
OL,15,Fopportunity to suspend the home birth
OL,16,Fservice when Mr Gillibrand rang a
OL,17,Fsecond time, at about 7am, after his
OL,18,Fwife's waters broke.
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@ZO]
