OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FThe inquest heard a midwife arrived at
OL,7,Fthe couple's home, about 15 to 20
OL,8,Fminutes' drive from the hospital, at
OL,9,Fabout 8:15am.
OL,11,FAfter 9am, Pippa's heart rate should
OL,12,Fhave been monitored every five minutes
OL,13,Fbut that was not done because midwives
OL,14,Fwere dealing with "competing
OL,15,Fpressures", including short staffing
OL,16,Fand laptops which were not working,
OL,17,Fthe court was told.
OL,26,@vD@SOUwD@JO]
