OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FThe coroner found that from 9:36am,
OL,7,Fafter difficulties in monitoring the
OL,8,Fheart rate became apparent, a decision
OL,9,Fshould have been made to transfer Mrs
OL,10,FGillibrand to hospital, where it was
OL,11,Flikely that a need for urgent delivery
OL,12,Fwould have been identified.
OL,14,FShe said: "Had Pippa been delivered
OL,15,Fearlier, on the balance of
OL,16,Fprobabilities she would not have died
OL,17,Fwhen she did."
OL,26,@vD@KOUyD@NO]
