OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FThe inquest heard Mrs Gillibrand was
OL,7,Ftransferred to hospital by ambulance
OL,8,Fafter a decision was made at 10am and
OL,9,FPippa was delivered by forceps.
OL,11,FShe was transferred to the neonatal
OL,12,Funit and later moved to Liverpool
OL,13,FWomen's Hospital but died on 5
OL,14,FSeptember after scans showed she had
OL,15,Fsuffered a "severe irreversible brain
OL,16,Finjury" due to a lack of oxygen.
OL,26,@wD@LOUxD@GO]
