OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FRecording a narrative conclusion, Ms
OL,7,FDavies said: "Pippa Gillibrand died as
OL,8,Fa result of a brain injury sustained
OL,9,Fdue to an avoidable delay in her
OL,10,Fdelivery."
OL,12,FShe said the Warrington hospital trust
OL,13,Fhad since remodelled its home birth
OL,14,Fservice, but at the time the community
OL,15,Fmidwives on the team assisted with
OL,16,Faround three labours a year.
OL,26,@oD@NOUrD@JO]
