OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FAli Kennah, chief nurse at Warrington
OL,7,Fand Halton Teaching Hospitals, said:
OL,8,F"We remain truly sorry for the
OL,9,Ffailures in the care that Mrs
OL,10,FGillibrand and Pippa received, and we
OL,11,Ffully accept the coroner's findings.
OL,13,F"Since this tragedy occurred, we have
OL,14,Fstrengthened our home birth service
OL,15,Fand have fully implemented all
OL,16,Frecommendations from an independent
OL,17,Freview. We will continue to make sure
OL,18,Fthat all lessons are learnt.
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/16
