OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,F"We would again like to extend our
OL,7,Fdeepest condolences to Mr and Mrs
OL,8,FGillibrand for their heartbreaking
OL,9,Floss."
OL,11,FMs Davies said a prevention of future
OL,12,Fdeaths report had been issued by a
OL,13,FManchester coroner following the
OL,14,Fdeaths of Jennifer Cahill, 34, and her
OL,15,Fchild Agnes Lily Wren Cahill, who died
OL,16,Fafter complications with a home birth.
OL,18,FBut she said she was not aware any
OL,19,Fnational guidance had been issued
OL,20,Fsince that report and was not assured
OL,21,Fthe issue had been resolved.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@FO]
