OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,FShe said she would issue her own
OL,7,Freport to raise concerns about the
OL,8,Flack of guidance for home birth
OL,9,Fservices and around data collection.
OL,11,FRebecca Cahill, from JMW solicitors,
OL,12,Fwho represented the family, said:
OL,13,F"What is clear from today's conclusion
OL,14,Fis that the family were failed from
OL,15,Fthe start.
OL,17,F"The circumstances arising on 25
OL,18,FAugust 2024 made the homebirth service
OL,19,Fmanifestly unsafe, and the service
OL,20,Fshould have been suspended when Vicky
OL,21,Fmade initial contact.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
