OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F398A1769620715
OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,F"Nevertheless, when Vicky's homebirth
OL,7,Fdid go ahead, she was failed again
OL,8,Fwhen basic guidelines were not
OL,9,Ffollowed, and concerns about Pippa's
OL,10,Fwellbeing were not immediately
OL,11,Frecognised by the attending midwives.
OL,13,F"The coroner has today concluded that
OL,14,Fthese failings resulted in an
OL,15,Favoidable delay in delivering Pippa
OL,16,Fresulting in her suffering a
OL,17,Fsignificant brain injury.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/16
