OL,3,CHome birth service played 'Russian
OL,4,Croulette' with lives, says bereaved dad
OL,6,F"If anything positive can be taken
OL,7,Ffrom this dreadful loss, it is that
OL,8,Fthe Trust recognises the failings in
OL,9,Fcare, and changes have already been
OL,10,Fimplemented which, we hope, will
OL,11,Fensure this does not happen to another
OL,12,Fbaby and another family.
OL,14,F"Pippa's family are grateful to
OL,15,Fcoroner for her thorough investigation.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/16
